To change timezone, copy one the correct time zone file to /etc/TZ. 
Read file "List_of_other_countries" lists for more possible time zone
settings. 

The file format is uLibC TZ string. More information on this can be 
found in 
http://www.sonoracomm.com/support/20-voice-support/107-uclibc-tz

WHEN CHANGING/MODIFYINNG THE TZ FILE IT IS IMPORTANT TO MAKE SURE THAT
THE FILE DOES NOT CONTAIN EXTRA SPACES OR (WINDOWN) LINEBREAKS!
